P_HTM[2885]="*(Yadapi maggasaṃyuttaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ, tadapi bojjhaṅgasaṃyuttaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)**(The Linked Discourses on Awakening Factors should be expanded just as the Linked Discourses on the Path.)*";
