P_HTM[5111]="*4. Esanāvaggo**Punaesanāvagga*";
P_HTM[5112]="*1-12. Pācīnādisuttadvādasakaṃ**159. Punaesanāvagga*";
P_HTM[5113]="*(Appamādavagga-balakaraṇīyavagga-esanāvaggā vitthāretabbā.)**(To be expanded as in SN 45.161–170, removal of greed version.)*";
