P_HTM[5160]="*Tathāgataṃ padaṃ kūṭaṃ,**The Realized One, footprint, roof peak,*";
P_HTM[5161]="*mūlaṃ sārena vassikaṃ;**roots, heartwood, jasmine,*";
P_HTM[5162]="*Rājā candimasūriyā,**monarch, sun and moon,*";
