P_HTM[5272]="*Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ uddhambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya pahānāya imāni pañca balāni bhāvetabbānī”ti.**These five powers should be developed for the direct knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these five higher fetters.”*";
