P_HTM[5930]="*Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:**The Buddha said to him:*";
P_HTM[5931]="*“katamā nu kho, ānanda, iddhi, katamo iddhipādo, katamā iddhipādabhāvanā, katamā iddhipādabhāvanāgāminī paṭipadā”ti?**“Ānanda, what is psychic power? What is the basis of psychic power? What is the development of the bases of psychic power? And what is the practice that leads to the development of the bases of psychic power?”*";
P_HTM[5932]="*Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā bhagavaṃnettikā … pe ….**“Our teachings are rooted in the Buddha. He is our guide and our refuge. …”*";
